thread.title: Kathleen Cruz
thread.title_full: Free My Paws reviewed by Kathleen Cruz

author: Kathleen Cruz
title: Kathleen Cruz
text: Free my paws was very helpful in getting my order completed. Was having a bit of a problem getting it done myself so I called left my name and # and they promptly got back to me and kindly helped me finish up my order. I recommend this company highly to anyone wanting to register their service animals. Prices are great as well.
